div.div: Dungeon Meshi: Senshi no Kantan Cooking!

Stop-motion short in honor of the 5th tankoubon going on sale. It features Senshi's hands trying to prepare a walking mushroom. It is the same walking mushroom as shown in the manga's 1st volume in the "Monster Tidbits" bonus chapter.

A strange turn of events leads the Dragon, Tohru, to work as Miss Kobayashi's maid. She occasionally (that's a lie, she often) causes trouble for her beloved Miss Kobayashi while blending into human society and splendidly (that's a lie, only mediocrely) carrying out her maid duties. Her fellow dragons, Kanna, Lucoa, Fafnir, and Elma all find their own places to fit in as well and enjoy interspecies interactions with the humans. Yet while they're all enjoying that laid-back and occasionally turbulent left, the threat of a new Dragon swoops down upon Miss Kobayashi.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Me ga Sametara Tougoku sareta Akujo datta @COMIC

Sophia, an apothecary who has been abused by the "Shameless Countess," wakes up one day to find herself in a prison cell. She has taken over the body of the bewitching beauty Violet, and the only clue she has is a note that says, "Please protect my body." Sophia is at a loss at first, but life in prison turns out to be more enjoyable than she expected! Meanwhile, Violet wakes up in Sophia's body, and starts working toward her goal, while showing off her new "arrogant bad-girl" attitude... This is a fantastical story of double revenge for a lady apothecary and a rare villainess, starting from opposite sides of the same coin!

(Source: Corona EX, translated)

Dumped after confessing to her first crush of three years, Ro-Sa Park falls for her second when the nation’s favorite Superpowered Police Officer, Do-Ryeong Han, swoops in to save her as she’s plummeting from a toppling building. A few years later, a mysterious villain called Blackdog appears, but Do-Ryeong notices something is not quite right. Will the world’s worst villain ever win the heart of the strongest hero in the country?
(Source: WEBTOONS, edited)
